Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:10.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}いつか　いつか　約束の空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:16.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}君となら　また　飛べるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:26.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}悔しくてツラくて眠れない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}誰にでもあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:37.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}そんな時は呼んで　駆けつけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}音の速さでね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:47.87,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}それがさだめ　でもね　あらがうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}君がホラ　笑ってね　くれるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:57.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}叶えたい夢　遠いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:04.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}いっしょなら出来るよ　無敵の勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:08.92,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}キラキラ光る　そのナミダ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:15.54,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}笑顔の魔法　でね　翼に変えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと　きっと　羽ばたけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:27.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}虹を超え　その先まで

Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:10.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}终有一天 终有一天 在约定的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:16.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}和你一起再次飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:26.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}因不甘和难过而无法入眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}谁都会有过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:37.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那时候请呼唤我 我会飞到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}以声音的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:47.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即便那就是命运 也要抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}因为看 你在对我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:57.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}想要实现的梦想 虽然还遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:04.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}一起的话 便能做到 以无敌的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:08.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那闪闪发光的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:15.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}用笑容的魔法变作翅膀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}一定 一定 能够展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:27.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}在那越过彩虹的彼端
;Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================================================ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:46.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ひとりじゃ　泣きそうな　広い空でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.21,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逃げないよ　真っ直ぐ立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.48,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}仲間と一緒に　Over Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:10.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}手のひらに風も　感じたのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:16.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もう　大丈夫　信じてジャンプしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:21.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}遠く浮かぶ雲　ひとっとびできるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:27.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}そんなドキドキ　想像できなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:33.25,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}みんなの明日の夢　守るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:39.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}勇気ありったけ　さあ　握り締めて飛びたて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:45.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ひとりじゃ　泣きそうな　大きい空でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:48.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}仲間がいれば　笑顔になれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:51.78,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ホラ　ただ奇跡じゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:56.69,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}約束したから　心に決めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:00.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逃げないよ　真っ直ぐ立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:09.81,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もっともっと素敵な世界のために　Over Sky

Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:46.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使是一个人会想要哭泣的广阔天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不要逃避  勇敢面对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.48,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}和伙伴们一起  Over Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:10.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}如果连掌心也能够感受到风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:16.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}已经没问题了  怀着信心起跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:21.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}遥远的浮云  一飞便能够便能够到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:27.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那样的兴奋  从来都无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:33.25,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}去守护大家明天的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:39.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}紧握所有的勇气起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:45.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使是一个人会想要哭泣的无垠天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:48.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}有同伴在  就会露出笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:51.78,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}看  这并不是什么奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:56.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}因为已经约定  因为已下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:00.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不会逃避  勇敢面对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:09.81,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为了更加美好的世界  Over Sky

;Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================================================Main



Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点  这所小学就能完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的复兴也进行得很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  朋友们不能来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥被…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以朋友们没法来学校了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 9 话\N架往明日之桥


Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现异型军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机进入战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎样的爬升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲太前面了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害很小  别乱了阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一发要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对桥做了什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会  全军攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到核心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把桥给！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  辛苦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫藤也已经基本适应震电了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我还想再训练下操控得更完美些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  就该是这气势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天表现得很活跃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是平时的佩琳的话  被少佐表扬后肯定会说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  少佐  就是这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多称赞我一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之类的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我克洛斯特尔曼一族\N代代相传的各种传家宝现在也只剩下这把骑士剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要把这个卖掉的话  就能凑够修复那座桥梁的资金了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  母亲  我该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊  突然扯着嗓子冲进别人的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…海…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明天大家一起到海边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  至少做下准备体操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然就泼水过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  就算说是训练  但绝对不允许掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没弄了  还请多加小心哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这项训练啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要来吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快给我跳下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真有你的呢  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  这都是多亏了您平日的训练指导…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防随时可能出现的突发情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久没尝试了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有佩琳在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你们所赐  连我都差点溺水了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好气派的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  听我说  海底下有一个箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还上着锁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像宝箱一样的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝箱吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这片阿德利亚海从古至今都是海上贸易很兴盛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一两个宝箱沉在海底也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  好像很有趣啊  丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  你们真的信宝箱这种蠢事的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是佩琳你说有的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底也只是可能性而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽奈  卢基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要有这宝物在 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥梁就能！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被吃了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你瞧  海底下不是有很多稀奇古怪的生物的么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王乌贼啦  大王海参啦  大王海星之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快去找她才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异型军？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁喵的说是异型军啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么想要宝物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊… 宝物… 到手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳！佩琳！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有听到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  桥梁完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳姐姐  多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面装了什么呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来动手的话就是小事一桩啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢  弗兰西斯卡·卢基尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这宝物的使用方式早就已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现了一个箱子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就代表里面的东西是如此重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面肯定装满了金银财宝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有几个箱子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么开都还是箱子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有出现宝物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能安静点  这个肯定是最后一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没有宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子们不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩 佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊

Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 佩琳在为了桥而努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从高卢回来样子就一直很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然钱还是不会这么轻易到手的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就算放弃传家之宝的骑士剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 好像有奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明明什么都没有里面却会发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近有做这种东西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和地图画的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳能读懂上面写的字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是拉丁语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读读拉丁语不过是良家淑女一点小嗜好而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  佩琳恢复精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽奈  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  像星空一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从洞窟入口射入的阳光被水面反射了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像哪一边都能通到里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想走散的话就跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢基尼不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说什么要去抓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了岩壁那边就没再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我记得宫藤她们训练之后也应该是去了岩壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙上的苔藓在发光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗  看得见地图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳加油  能看得懂地图的就只有佩琳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着从这里一直往前走就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不安全嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前有谁走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进到这里面去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进哪边了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分开太危险了  从右边去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人费心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是像探险一样真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是人工造的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用作基地的地方  原本也是古代魔女的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这洞窟也是它的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是很了不起的壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的老前辈的技术么  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事怎么都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  没事吗美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气味是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 不是血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是红酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 美绪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…少佐  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜有点不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能指挥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那可怕的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是古代人的怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办吧  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着啊  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要走到哪儿去才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧卢基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点  在这光芒的前方一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是地图上画的宝贝的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错的  终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的石像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有镰仓大佛那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像有点可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  在那个石像的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里应该沉睡着宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  宝贝在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  孩子们的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢基尼好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石…石像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在架上桥之前  是不能放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是赤手空拳的确不太妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  母亲大人  还有高卢的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是宝物的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是香草…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁香还有月桂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥勒冈 藏红花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这个是胡椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这就是宝物…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么少佐会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这竟然就是我在找的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都只是香辛料而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的话也许是贵重的财产  现在全都是简单就能到手的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西根本没法成为高卢的复兴资金来源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那份为高卢着想的心  才是最重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  卢基尼在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫藤她们也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧  哈特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们在干啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说那里是古代的遗迹  魔女为了保卫宝物而施的魔法大概还存留着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击佩琳的说不定就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事真是让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这个  寄给佩琳的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是从高卢寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起建造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合大家的力量建起的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说不定就是真正的复兴呢  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也要尽快打倒异形军  然后再回高卢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  到时我会给你们做向导的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤火辣辣的疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法穿裤子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  真是谜团众多的基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  中佐怎么了？


Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哈特曼  你的击坠数是多少架来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3  不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  Strike Witches 2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500 overs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是多少架啊…
